version_description: This is the acoustic/piano version of Bad Romance, as performed by Lady Gaga live at The Rainbow Room (seen in Gaga: Five Foot Two).
I just improved it a bit, I hope you like them and will help them.
These chords are the ones used in her live performance at the Rainbow Room for Tony Bennett's 90th birthday.

performance.name: Live at Rainbow Room
performance.comment: Version taken from "Gaga: Five Foot Two" (2017) documentary

version_description: It's the first original by me.
The other version is somewhat acceptable but incomplete, this is a more complete/proper version of the tab. No Capo is required to play this version. this track is off the album JOANNE by Lady Gaga.
